import { Component,OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { FormsModule } from '@angular/forms'; @Component({ selector: 'app-employeeform', templateUrl: './employeeform.component.html', styleUrls: ['./employeeform.component.css'] }) export class EmployeeformComponent implements OnInit { formData = { name: '', designation: '', location: '', salary: '' }; constructor() { } ngOnInit(): void { } submitForm(form: any) { alert('Form submitted'); } }

Employee Form

Name is required.
Designation is required.
Location is required.
Salary is required.
